    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Welcome to IDeal, a 3D horror game where you have to escape from a school with unknown anomalies.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Escape safely from 'Jain High School' by following guidelines and rules of conduct. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Approach with caution, unless you </i><strong>■▅■▊ ▅■▊ ■▅▊ ■ ■ ■▅▊</strong><i>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning: If you see this warning, we recommend that you read it carefully.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Careless behaviors can lead to the following consequences.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >minor injury with little bleeding or wound</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >serious life-threatening injuries</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▊■▆■▊▆■▆■▊■ (■▊■▆▊)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >0. You are at Jain High School. We repeat. <br>You are at Jain High School now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Jain High School manages students thoroughly. <br>All students are not allowed to leave school until the bell rings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. In order to leave the school, you have to ring the school bell from the broadcast room. <br>For more information, press [tab] to read the Checklist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Be sure to check the bulletin board next to the main gate before entering the school. <br>You can check the rules of conduct, which will keep you alive while exploring the school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. If it is deemed impossible to escape, please check inside your pocket. <br>There will be a special pill prepared for the last moment. <br>We strongly recommend that you take the pill for your own sake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please double check if you understood all the instructions again before entering the school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We <strong>■▊ ■■▆▊</strong> wish you a safe return.</p>",
